<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880121-0121 </DOCNO><HL> LTV Wins 2 NASA Contracts </HL><SO> </SO><CO> GOVMT LTV </CO><DATELINE> DALLAS  </DATELINE><TEXT>   LTV Corp. said its Missiles andamp; Electronics Group received two contracts from the National Aeronautics and Space Administration for work on launches of the Scout space launch vehicle.    The NASA contracts, which together total $30.4 million, call for LTV to provide ground crews and technical services for all Scout launches in 1988 and 1989.    LTV is a defense contractor and electronics and steelmaking concern. </TEXT></DOC>